OL,5, An autistic pensioner was left living  
OL,6, on dog food after his benefits were    
OL,7, stopped, according to the Local        
OL,8, Government Ombudsman (LGO).            
OL,10,FThe man was wrongly denied emergency   
OL,11,Ffinancial support by East Riding       
OL,12,FCouncil, the organisation ruled.       
OL,14,FDisruption to his support payments     
OL,15,Fmeant the man could not afford to eat  
OL,16,For pay his utility bills.              
OL,18,FThe council agreed to apologise to the 
OL,19,Fman and find out if he was entitled to 
OL,20,Fany backdated support payments.        
